                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <br/>
                        <strong>Attention: </strong>
                        <span t-field="o.attention_id"/>
                        <br/>
                        <strong>Tel No: </strong>
                        <span t-field="o.telno"/>
                        <br/>
                        <strong>Fax No: </strong>
                        <span t-field="o.faxno"/>
                        <br/>

                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-4" style="font-size:13px;">
                        <h3>
                            <strong>Quotation</strong>
